# Philip Builds Studio AI backend environment names (EXAMPLE ONLY)
# Set these in Vercel Project Settings. Never commit a real .env file.
# GitHub Pages does not read these; only the server-side api/chat.js function does.

# Required to enable real model replies. Use one server-side key:
# - OPENAI_API_KEY
# - AI_API_KEY
# - OPENROUTER_API_KEY
# - AI_PROVIDER_API_KEY (legacy fallback)

# Optional server-side config:
# - AI_BASE_URL defaults to https://api.openai.com/v1
# - AI_MODEL defaults to gpt-4o-mini
